Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.41,0:02:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣的事要問多少次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果距離很遠的話  你就會在那待10天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個  看店的人手找好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我的堂親由紀江週末會來幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平時呢？不就只有祖母一個人了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧  拿個冠軍也未嘗不可哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,獲…獲得全國冠軍  這也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.72,0:03:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  是你的話  只要和小晴繪在一起就會有希望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小晴繪在出場的全國比賽  你全都看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最後她輸掉的時候  你還大哭了一場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  怎麼還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在地區預賽上  真是好久不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼開心的打著麻將的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一邊照看著店面  一邊一直看著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.87,0:03:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊  要拿到冠軍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望打得盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.19,0:04:08.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才是二回戰而已  不能在這裏輸掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊  灼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要注意一下那個戰績不明的劍谷一年級的正式隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿知賀高年級的三人都有些奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我還沒能分析出她的打牌傾向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,副將戰  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子讓人很難捉摸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誤差水平看起來相當分散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使她有什麼偏好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算上地區和全國賽  我們也只有5場比賽的數據啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只靠這些數據  就能分析出打牌傾向的松實姐妹才更為異常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她在比賽中確實有些奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  數據也並非萬能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,浩子  沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子  這種情況下不管怎樣都會想去研究對手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歸根結底她是個研究者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然將第三位的接力棒傳給了一年級的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我代表沒用的高年級生在此謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…沒  沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小梢  你的對手可是千里山的江口夕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是沒辦法的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還是很有可能逆轉奪回第二位的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  小友香的話一定可以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閒家2000  莊家4000
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  友香好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然無法正座啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  只是東一局就不行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣沒問題吧  真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是歸國子女啊  能夠融入我們之中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該搞好關係的是哪個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定可能是我們才對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想比現在前行得更遠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是循規蹈矩可能是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這麼覺得的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,立直！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才剛三向聽  棄和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:15.74,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（三向聴(さんちゃんてん)：在手中的牌最少要换三张才能达至听牌）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃  先解除你的一發
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.44,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（解除一发：一発消し(いっぱつけし)，以吃碰杠的方式破坏一发的条件，\N即使立直者能立即自摸也拿不到一发的番数）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸  每人8000
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莊家倍滿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又落到第三了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,劍谷的森垣選手  一下子完成了莊家倍滿自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一口氣上升至第二位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.47,0:07:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小友香  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  她做到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不奪回失點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閒家1300  莊家2600
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:32.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,副將戰  結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千里山的壓倒性優勢依舊不變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.90,0:08:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  憑借森垣的努力奮鬥  劍谷升至了第二位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,No——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二位的競爭會集中在劍谷和阿知賀之間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,越谷女子的點數形勢相當嚴峻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能觸及到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,時不時看到的令人無法捉摸的出牌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果看更多的牌譜  就能明白她的意圖了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一個值得好好研究的素材
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,努力了呢  灼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下面就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  勝負懸念將被帶到大將賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小穩  拜託了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,12000
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿知賀女子  高鴨穩乃  點了別家的暗聽跳滿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.24,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（暗听(ダマ)：在门清的情况下，没有宣告立直的听牌）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,後半戰南三局出現這種情況將會十分致命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第八巡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:10:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說是最後一次莊家局  是不是有點放鬆警惕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終於到了大將戰後半終盤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最後的一局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔哇  唔哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,配牌也很糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:19.40,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（配牌(はいぱい)：牌局开始时摸入的13张牌）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小穩…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.97,0:10:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能放棄！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,終盤開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,親家的千里山基本已經確保了半決賽的出戰資格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此不管是和牌還是流局都將宣告比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:59.31,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（流局(りゅうきょく)：当没有剩下可以摸的牌但仍然没有人能和牌，\N即为流局，该局结束进入下一局）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:00.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會出現連莊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.54,0:11:03.04,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（連荘(れんちゃん)：庄家和牌或者流局听牌时庄家权会保留，\N但如果是最后一场比赛的最后一局而庄家是第一名，则不会进行连庄）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此這就是最後一局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.42,0:11:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二位的劍谷目前是93600點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,緊跟其後的第三位的阿知賀女子是81700點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿知賀要完成逆轉需要自摸跳滿以上的點數
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直擊則需要6400點以上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.88,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（直撃(ちょくげき)：直接点和指定的对象，以达成排名上的逆转）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  誰能獲得第二位進軍半決賽呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後  已經被遠遠甩開的越谷女子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能讓我們看看你們的底力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以逆轉局勢的高分暗聽跳滿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果拿到低得分的4索的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使立直了  如果沒有裏寶牌也無法逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果流局了  比賽就會立即結束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在暗聽下等待最後的1索了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍遲疑後才打出了手中的紅5
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.09,0:11:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來聽牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使役滿  我們的第一位也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,低得分牌？這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.89,0:12:02.78,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（低得分牌：安目(やすめ)，多面听时较低分的一张听牌）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能撐過這一局  就能進軍半決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,同巡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.40,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（同巡(どうじゅん)：同巡振听，放过第一次点和后，\N自己摸牌前不可以和第二次点和的规则）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.35,0:12:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在沒有辦法和牌的情況下  最後的一張高得分牌被打出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.86,0:12:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們…要在這裏敗退了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小穩不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家應該是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話  果然將是千里山和劍谷進入半決賽了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  還沒有結束的時候不要說這種話啊  解說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看那傢伙的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反倒是好戲即將上演了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三暗刻…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也考慮過這種變化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是牌河裏已經有兩枚二索  一枚一萬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.97,0:13:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能自摸到剩下的唯一一枚一萬的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…才剛說完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自摸三暗刻也沒有機會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,七對子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩枚寶牌  所以自摸是滿貫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他家放銃的話只有6400
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有直擊劍谷才能追上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能過吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,點和！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,6400！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翻山的七對子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.78,0:15:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正正好好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第三位阿知賀女子的高鴨選手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以6400點直擊第二位劍谷的安福選手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在最終局完成逆轉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿知賀女子  最終位列第二！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進入半決賽的是北大阪代表千里山女子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以及奈良代表阿知賀女子學院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明在臨結束的時候還點了個默聽跳滿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個不肯放棄的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊  我可不會祝賀你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,半決賽也確定會和阿知賀女子再戰一場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好像很開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.22,0:16:07.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對那個打保齡球的孩子就那麼在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.62,0:16:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只…只不過是研究的素材了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…我覺得下次我們恐怕是沒有空閒去顧及那些孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.47,0:16:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高中聯賽第五天  A賽區第二輪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兵庫代表劍谷高校與琦玉代表越谷女子雖然經過頑強的奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾還是就此雙雙敗退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慶祝躋身8強！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慶祝！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暫且能放心了呢  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:52.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大人的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只是麥茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天就是不一樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,興奮最好也要有個限度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,後天可就不好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你們被千里山甩開多少點？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,9萬點…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,後天的半決賽上  還將出現比千里山更強勁的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白…白糸台…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.80,0:17:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請看向這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先祝賀你們進入半決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,史上首次三連霸已經近在眼前  請問有什麼感想？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.29,0:17:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三連霸是我們的首要目標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以後天的半決賽我們是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也涌現出很多強勁的隊伍  我非常期待接下來的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們將全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請大家多多支持！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:00.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙的職業笑容還是那麼過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是真的發自內心感謝著很多人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並沒有說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…跟平時差太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之三連霸肯定是沒有問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果千里山裏有荒川憩和愛宕洋榎的話說不定還有得一拼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冠軍會是白糸台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這毫無疑問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天甩開你們9萬點差的千里山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以及公認在此之上的白糸台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有福岡的強豪新道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.86,0:18:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以這三隊為對手  不拿到第二位的話就進不了決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…雖然已經知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從報導輿論來看  我們想進軍決賽說好聽點是令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說難聽點就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下來去參加教練會議  然後就在外面吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家享受一下客房服務  今天就好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得晴繪聲音有些顫抖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法啊  接下來就是「那場半決賽」了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.54,0:19:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,半決賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小晴沒能逾越的障礙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好想吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:19:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好想吃拉麵！拉麵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼突然想到拉麵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿～能吃到貨真價實的東京拉麵的機會可不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是赤土老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晴繪和…和誰來著  那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.67,0:20:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是熊倉教練啊  在福岡時擔任教練的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  說起來小穩你的眼神還是那麼好使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  為什麼我要藏起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概因為剛剛惹她生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進軍職業的事情怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:54.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:21:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帶領學生闖入全國半決賽已經提升了對你的評價哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.80,0:21:05.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晚些時候我會郵件正式答覆的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.26,0:21:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晴繪不會是把我們當作棋子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.38,0:21:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小晴她不可能做那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  她不也說了我們被甩開那麼大點差  下次已經贏不了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經被拋棄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為我…因為我被搶走了太多點數…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.47,0:21:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那這個軟軟的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼憑空冒出來一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.96,0:21:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦  小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕的有些急  不小心撞到人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…都是我自己沒有站穩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.48,0:22:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:12.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.03,0:22:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人應該是…東橫同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  為什麼知道我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在那間豪宅裏看過長野地區的比賽錄像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在副將戰比和與透華得點還要高的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別指著人家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是大胸同學的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,透華同學說過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶴賀學園消失的一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隱身小桃…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:47.11,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}頂点まであと一息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:53.33,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}{\fad(0,300)}アガリーち　All Right!!　咲き誇れ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:23:00.54,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}東から西まで　北から南まで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:06.25,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}走り抜ける　四方八方　全身全霊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:11.25,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}握るも捨てるも　ドキドキ選択
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:13.76,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}センチメンタルに　ドヤッと!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:16.58,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}また騒ごうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:18.24,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}こっちでも　(牌!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:19.59,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}あっちでも　(牌!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:22.23,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}偶然でも　幸運でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:24.67,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}引き寄せて　乗っちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:27.70,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}せい!　a-c-h-i-g-a　れっつごー!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:30.24,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}(まーじゃんぱにっくもういちど　Here we Go!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:32.88,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}あの舞台を転げ回って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:35.64,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}奏でちゃってよ、My セレナーデ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:38.20,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}星屑みたいキラキラって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:41.01,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}四角い箱の中　夢いっぱい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:43.69,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}楽しくなってきちゃったね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:46.37,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}くるくる回る、ターン to ターン
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:49.10,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}駆け引き、勝ち負け、あの子に繋いで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.17,0:23:54.23,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}この草原駆け抜けよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:56.81,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}徹底的　射程距離圈內
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:24:02.56,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}{\fad(0,500)}ここ一番　ぞっくぞく打ち上がれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.77,0:22:47.11,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}距離頂點還差一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:53.33,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}{\fad(0,300)}和牌立直　All Right!!　盡情綻放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:23:00.54,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}由東至西　自北向南
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.62,0:23:06.25,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}奔跑穿越四面八方　全心全力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:11.25,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}不管是留牌還是棄牌　都是心跳的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:13.76,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}敏感過後一躍而上!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:16.58,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}再一起去放縱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:18.24,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}這裏也好　(牌!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:19.59,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}那裏也好　(牌!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:22.23,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}偶然也好　幸運也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:24.67,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}趁勢而上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:27.70,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}Say!  a-c-h-i-g-a  Let's Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:30.24,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}(麻將恐慌　再次來襲　Here we Go!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:32.88,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}翻轉著那舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:35.64,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}奏響起這首　My Serenade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:38.20,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}像那群星般閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.27,0:23:41.01,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}在這四角的桌面中　滿載夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:43.69,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}逐漸變得快樂起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:46.37,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}一輪接著一輪　來來回回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:49.10,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}策略手段　勝敗輸贏　牽起那雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.17,0:23:54.23,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}全力穿越過這片草原吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:56.81,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}在這徹底的打擊範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.93,0:24:02.56,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}{\fad(0,500)}讓我們盡情地不斷宣洩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.06,0:24:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小穩你有多少件那種運動衫？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.33,0:24:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…長袖和無袖的  一件兩件三件…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶爾也試試其它的打扮吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.41,0:24:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的衣服可以稍微借你一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.99,0:24:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那個還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.48,0:24:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.46,0:24:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尺寸不合…
